room_title: Escape room "Chain Reaction" by Key and Code Escape Rooms in Reno
review: Had an amazing time tonight trying to Escape the Chain Reaction room! Can't wait to go back and see if I can get out!

room_title: Escape room "Chain Reaction" by Key and Code Escape Rooms in Reno
review: We did Chain Reaction and loved it! Difficulty was appropriate for our group of 8 (introducing 2 to the puzzle room experience). Quality and theme are as good as their competition. We will be back to complete the other puzzles!
